<% provide :title, "Email Lists" %>

<p>Your list of email addresses appears below, if the box is empty then now email addresses could be found.</p>

<div style="border-style: solid; border-color: black; border-width: 2px; width: 50%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; min-height: 2em;"><pre>
<%- @emails.each_with_index do |email, index| %>
<%= email %><%= ', ' unless index == (@emails.size - 1) %>
<%- end %>
</pre></div>
